Name: Hidden Objects - Cartoon Fantasy
About the game: Are you ready to test your eyes with Hidden Objects - Cartoon Fantasy, your seek and find skills will be challenged like never before. Develops your secret seeker skill to find objects. This is a puzzle game similar to Hidden Object games, in which you have to find the objects while the clock is ticking. Hidden Objects - Cartoon Fantasy is not only a visually satisfying but also mentally and entertaining experience after hours of stressful work. If you are looking for a game to test your talent and practice your ability to observe. This is a game for all ages. Children can play to improve their attention capacity and visual ability. Elderly people also can play as an attention and concentration practice. Everyone will have a great time, no matter your age!. Features: - 3 Game Modes: Easy, Normal, Hard - 400 Beautiful icons to find - Play a cool and relaxed match, with no time countdown - Boost your brainpower and discernment
